  "commit_message": "feat(ui): notifications — optimistic-locking client side\n\nPairs with rearm-saas f00014ce. Three forms now capture the row's\n@Version revision on Edit-load and round-trip it as expectedRevision\non the upsert; the backend's \"Conflict:\" error surfaces with a Reload\nfrom server affordance so the operator can refresh the form with the\nlatest state before retrying instead of staring at a generic save-failed\ntoast.\n\nUI changes:\n\n- ChannelRow / SubscriptionRow add revision: number; ChannelGroupRow\n  alr",
